21/*
22
23@deftypefn Supplemental void* mempcpy (void *@var{out}, const void *@var{in}, @
24 size_t @var{length})
25
26Copies @var{length} bytes from memory region @var{in} to region
27@var{out}. Returns a pointer to @var{out} + @var{length}.
28
29@end deftypefn
30
31*/
32
33#include <ansidecl.h>
34#include <stddef.h>
35
36extern PTR memcpy (PTR, const PTR, size_t);
37
38PTR
39mempcpy (PTR dst, const PTR src, size_t len)
40{
41 return (char *) memcpy (dst, src, len) + len;
42}
